     $$
       Q(A) = PQ(B)P^{-1}
     $$
     donc
     $$
       Q(A) = 0_{n} \iff  PQ(B)P^{-1} = 0 \iff  Q(B) = 0
     $$
     Ainsi, $\pi_{A} = \pi_{B}$.
